snippet.title: Public TV
snippet.description: This is an official channel of Public TV Kannada news channel. The slogan is "Yaara Aasthiyoo Alla, Idu Nimma TV". Public TV launched on 12 February 2012. HR Ranganath and His Young team's dream Venture.. A news Channel For the people... Not Owned by any Politician, or Businessman. Its News channel of a true Journalist.
